'''王大仁'''（{{Lang-en|Alexander Wang}}，{{bd|1983年|12月26日|||catIdx=Wang}}），[[美国|美国]][[时装设计师|时装设计师]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Alexander Wang - Biography |url=https://www.businessoffashion.com/community/people/alexander-wang |publisher=The Business of Fashion |accessdate=2021-02-28 |language=en |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903063316/https://www.businessoffashion.com/community/people/alexander-wang |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Biography – Alexander Wang |url=http://www.alexanderwang.com/studio/biography |publisher=Alexander Wang |accessdate=2021-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325103129/http://www.alexanderwang.com/studio/biography |archivedate=2012-03-25 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Sarah Karmali |title=Alexander Wang Named Balenciaga Creative Director |url=https://www.vogue.co.uk/article/alexander-wang-balenciaga-creative-director-confirmed |publisher=[[时尚_(Vogue)|时尚（英国版）]] |accessdate=2021-02-28 |language=en |archive-date=2016-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730035752/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/2012/11/30/alexander-wang-balenciaga-creative-director-confirmed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在2005年开创了“{{lang|en|Alexander Wang}}”品牌并于2008年获得{{Link-en|美国时装设计师协会|Council of Fashion Designers of America|CFDA}}{{\}}[[时尚_(Vogue)|VOGUE]]时尚基金奖。曾担任[[巴黎世家|巴黎世家]]的设计总监。王大仁的设计风格以凸显都市风及善用黑色闻名。

== 早年境况 ==
王大仁于1983年12月26日出身在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[旧金山市|旧金山市]]，他和他的哥哥王大鲲（{{lang|en|Dennis W}}ang）一起长大<ref>{{cite web |author1=刘隽 |title=Alexander Wang全面掌控同名品牌公司，董事会主席、CEO、创意总监三职合一 |url=https://luxe.co/post/42285 |publisher=华丽志 |accessdate=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2017-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016102012/http://luxe.co/post/42285 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Elsa de Berker |title=Alexander Wang voices pride at his immigrant roots as he shows spring 2019 collection in New York |url=https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/fashion-beauty/article/2149100/alexander-wang-voices-pride-his-immigrant-roots-he-shows |publisher=[[南华早报|南华早报]] |accessdate=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2018-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610042043/https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/fashion-beauty/article/2149100/alexander-wang-voices-pride-his-immigrant-roots-he-shows |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Alexander Wang Becomes CEO and Chairman of His Namesake Brand |url=https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/finance/alexander-wang-becomes-ceo-and-chairman-of-his-namesake-brand |publisher=The Business of Fashion |accessdate=2021-02-28}}</ref>。王大仁表示他并不会说[[普通话|普通话]]，同时他也和[[王薇薇|王薇薇]]没有亲属关系<ref>{{cite web |author1=Dhani Mau |title=Alexander wang says he doesn't speak mandarin, is 'doing something quite different' at balenciaga |url=https://fashionista.com/2013/02/alexander-wang-doesnt-speak-mandarin-is-doing-something-quite-different-at-balenciaga |accessdate=2021-02-28}}</ref>。

王大仁的小学和初中都是在加利福尼亚州[[聖荷西_(加利福尼亞州)|圣何塞]]的{{Link-en|哈克学校|Harker School}}度过<ref>{{cite web |author1=Zach Jones |title=Alumnus Wang Named to Forbes 30 Under 30: Art & Design for Award-Winning Lifestyle Brand |url=https://news.harker.org/alumnus-wang-named-to-forbes-30-under-30-art-design-for-award-winning-lifestyle-brand/ |publisher={{Link-en|哈克学校|Harker School}} |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119220802/https://news.harker.org/alumnus-wang-named-to-forbes-30-under-30-art-design-for-award-winning-lifestyle-brand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。九年级时，他升入[[圆石滩|圆石滩]]的{{Link-en|史蒂文森学校|Stevenson School}}就读，但随后转校至旧金山的{{Link-en|德鲁学校|Drew School}}并在这里高中毕业。在15岁那年，王大仁参加了[[中央聖馬丁藝術與設計學院|中央圣马丁学院]]的一个暑期设计培训项目<ref>{{cite web |author1=Karizza Sanchez |title=10 Things You Didn’t Know About Alexander Wang |url=https://www.complex.com/style/2012/12/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-alexander-wang/ |publisher=Complex |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2018-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620002311/https://www.complex.com/style/2012/12/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-alexander-wang/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

18岁时，王大仁搬家到了[[纽约市|纽约市]]并在[[帕森设计学院|帕森设计学院]]就读大学课程<ref name="NYMag">{{cite web |title=Alexander Wang - Designer Fashion Label |url=http://nymag.com/fashion/fashionshows/designers/bios/alexanderwang/ |publisher=[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519105422/http://nymag.com/fashion/fashionshows/designers/bios/alexanderwang/ |archivedate=2012-05-19}}</ref>。但是在就读帕森两年后，王大仁选择离开了学校并开始创业，因此他并没有从大学毕业<ref>{{cite web |title=Alexander Wang: Too Cool for School |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/alexander-wang-too-cool-for-school-1809343.html |publisher=[[独立报|独立报]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111005511/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/alexander-wang-too-cool-for-school-1809343.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 职业生涯 ==
=== 发展初期 ===
在[[帕森设计学院|帕森设计学院]]就读两年后，王大仁决定在2005年开创自己的[[時尚設計|时尚品牌]]；该品牌最初主要是针织衫系列。2007年秋季，王大仁首次在[[纽约时装周|纽约时装周]]推出了他的完整女装成衣系列。2008年，他获得了由{{Link-en|美国时装设计师协会|Council of Fashion Designers of America}}和《[[时尚_(Vogue)|时尚杂志]]》联合颁发的时尚基金奖并赢得了2万美元用以扩张他的时尚业务<ref name="NYMag" />。同年，王大仁发表了他的第一个手袋系列。

在接连推出以黑色为主要色调的2008年秋季系列<ref>{{cite web |title=Alexander Wang Fall 2008 Ready-to-Wear Collection |url=http://www.style.com/fashionshows/complete/F2008RTW-AWANG |publisher=Style.com |accessdate=2021-03-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510173022/http://www.style.com/fashionshows/complete/F2008RTW-AWANG |archivedate=2012-05-10 |language=en}}</ref>和以亮色（例如橙色、灰紫色、水绿色和深粉色）为主色调的2009年春季系列之后<ref>{{cite web |author1=Meenal Mistry |title=Alexander Wang Spring 2009 Ready-to-Wear Collection |url=http://www.style.com/fashionshows/review/S2009RTW-AWANG/ |publisher=Style.com |accessdate=2021-03-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312172222/http://www.style.com/fashionshows/review/S2009RTW-AWANG/ |archivedate=2012-03-12 |language=en |date=2008-09-06}}</ref>，王大仁的设计又恢复以黑色面料为主的风格，同时他的出色剪裁得到了广泛赞誉。

