== 个人生活 ==
王大仁是一名[[男同性恋者|男同性恋者]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Anna Coren |title=Interview with Fashion Designer Alexander Wang |url=http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/1206/08/ta.01.html |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224060154/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/1206/08/ta.01.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时也是[[LGBTQ|LGBTQ]]社群的狂热支持者<ref>{{cite web |title=‘My First Gay Bar’: Rachel Maddow, Andy Cohen and Others Share Their Coming-Out Stories |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/23/fashion/my-first-gay-bar-rosie-odonnell-rachel-maddow-alexander-wang-andy-cohen-share.html |publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320151413/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/23/fashion/my-first-gay-bar-rosie-odonnell-rachel-maddow-alexander-wang-andy-cohen-share.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年，他与[[安全套|安全套]]厂商{{Link-en|特洛伊 (品牌)|Trojan (brand)|特洛伊}}联名推出了限量版的“{{lang|en|Protect Your Wang}}”胶囊系列，用以支持LGBT社群及举办[[同志骄傲|同志骄傲]]庆典<ref>{{cite web |author1=Lindsey Ellefson |title=Pride 2018: Alexander Wang sends a powerful message about sexual health in the LGBT community |url=https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/alexander-wang-trojan-condoms-protect-your-wang/index.html |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109092022/https://edition.cnn.com/style/article/alexander-wang-trojan-condoms-protect-your-wang/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

王大仁热衷举行派对的形象也广为人知，他也因此举办过许多明星云集的派对。例如：臭名昭著加油站派对<ref>{{cite web |author1=Steff Yotka |title=“You’ve Never Seen Anything Like This”: Remembering Alexander Wang’s Infamous Gas Station Party, 10 Years Later |url=https://www.vogue.com/article/remembering-alexander-wang-spring-2010-gas-station-party |publisher=[[时尚_(Vogue)|时尚]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124065648/https://www.vogue.com/article/remembering-alexander-wang-spring-2010-gas-station-party |dead-url=no }}</ref>、宝格丽×王大仁派对<ref>{{cite web |author1=Ian Malone |title=Ain’t No Party Like an Alexander Wang Party! A Look Inside the Designer’s Tequila-, Champagne-, and Vodka-Soaked After-Party |url=https://www.vogue.com/slideshow/alexander-wang-after-party |publisher=[[时尚_(Vogue)|时尚]] |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926160811/https://www.vogue.com/slideshow/alexander-wang-after-party |dead-url=no }}</ref>、纽约时尚周派对<ref>{{cite web |author1=Emilia Petrarca |title=Alexander Wang Is the Only One Still Partying |url=https://www.thecut.com/2019/02/alexander-wang-new-york-fashion-week-party.html |publisher=The Cut |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126084831/https://www.thecut.com/2019/02/alexander-wang-new-york-fashion-week-party.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>等。

王大仁目前居住在[[纽约市|纽约市]]，但是他在[[纽约州|纽约州]]多地拥有房产，例如[[韦斯特切斯特县|韦斯特切斯特县]]和[[雀兒喜_(紐約)|切尔西]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andrea Park |title=Alexander Wang Buys Midcentury Pavilion-Style House in Westchester County |url=https://www.architecturaldigest.com/story/alexander-wang-buys-midcentury-pavilion-style-house |publisher={{Link-en|建筑文摘|Architectural Digest}} |accessdate=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302074445/https://www.architecturaldigest.com/story/alexander-wang-buys-midcentury-pavilion-style-house |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

